               <p>THOMAS JONES. I <rs id="t18271025-187-viclabel1075" type="occupation">work at an iron-foundry</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271025-187-victim959 t18271025-187-viclabel1075"></join>. On the 9th of October I missed my trousers from <placeName id="t18271025-187-crimeloc1076">Brown-court</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18271025-187-crimeloc1076" type="placeName" value="Brown-court"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18271025-187-crimeloc1076" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271025-187-off1073 t18271025-187-crimeloc1076"></join>, where I and the prisoner lodged; I left them safe about six o'clock on the morning of the 7th, and left him in bed - he slept with me, and worked at the same place; I never allowed him to wear or pawn my clothes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18271025-187-person960">
                  JOHN 
                  O'BRIEN
               <interp inst="t18271025-187-person960" type="surname" value="O'BRIEN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18271025-187-person960" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18271025-187-person960" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an iron-founder. The prisoner and prosecutor both lodged at our house - I called them both up; the prisoner came down last; I called to ask if he was not going to work; he came down, and went out- he did not come to work, and the trousers were missed; when he was taken he offered me the duplicate, and 4s. 6d.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18271025-187-person961">
